\par Vi\'d6c s\'f6 d\'f4ng thi\'d5t b\'de \'aeo m\'c9u \'ae\'d3 hi\'d6u chu\'c8n \'ae\'e9 suy gi\'b6m ban \'ae\'c7u ph\'b6i tu\'a9n theo \'ae\'f3ng h\'ad\'edng d\'c9n v\'d2 khai th\'b8c v\'b5 s\'f6 d\'f4ng c\'f1a thi\'d5t b\'de n\'b5y.
\par 
